# System Architecture

This repository follows an **AI-assisted, spec-driven development workflow**.

Features are implemented using **Clean Architecture**, **CQRS**, and **Vertical Slice Architecture**.

The system is designed to support **microservice-oriented architecture** while maintaining a clean and maintainable codebase.

